  
  EMAP :    Procedures (and functions) relating to exposure maps

    MAKEMOI     :   Create a modified instrument (MOI) bit map
    MOI_BOX     :   Calculate the x and y positions of all pixels which lie
                    both within a specified rectangle and within the limits 
                    of the MOI bit map. Used in MAKEMOI.
    MOI_LIMIT_PIX : Select the x and y positions of all pixels which lie
                    within the limits of the MOI bit map and also within a
                    specified annulus. Used in MAKEMOI.

